{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/6082", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/6082/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/6082/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/6082/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/6082", "id": 309533682, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MTc4MTY1NjIz", "number": 6082, "title": "Make global variable in Storage.cpp static", "user": {"login": "goldsborough", "id": 6429851, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0Mjk4NTE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/6429851?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough", "html_url": "https://github.com/goldsborough", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/goldsborough/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 2, "created_at": "2018-03-28T21:12:20Z", "updated_at": "2018-11-23T15:41:15Z", "closed_at": "2018-03-28T21:42:31Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/pulls/6082", "html_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/6082", "diff_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/6082.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/6082.patch"}, "body_html": "<p>We ran into issues where <code>THStorage_(copy_functions)</code> was being re-initialized upon <code>dlopen()</code>. Declaring it <code>static</code> rather than <code>extern</code> fixes the problem and is also better practice.</p>\n<p>Since there were so many <code>static</code> things, I put them all into an anonymous namespace, which has the same effect.</p>\n<p><a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=655866\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/colesbury\">@colesbury</a> <a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=5702157\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/adamlerer\">@adamlerer</a></p>", "body_text": "We ran into issues where THStorage_(copy_functions) was being re-initialized upon dlopen(). Declaring it static rather than extern fixes the problem and is also better practice.\nSince there were so many static things, I put them all into an anonymous namespace, which has the same effect.\n@colesbury @adamlerer", "body": "We ran into issues where `THStorage_(copy_functions)` was being re-initialized upon `dlopen()`. Declaring it `static` rather than `extern` fixes the problem and is also better practice.\r\n\r\nSince there were so many `static` things, I put them all into an anonymous namespace, which has the same effect.\r\n\r\n@colesbury @adamlerer "}